1.connect to a wired internet connection 
2.sudo apt-update 
3.sudo apt install -y dkms git
4.git clone https://github.com/anantbarthwal/Realtek-RTL8821CE-WiFi-Driver-on-Ubuntu-20.04.git
DICONNECT INTERNET
5.cd rtl8821ce
6.sudo ./dkms-install.sh
7.sudo modprobe 8821ce


P.S. Secure Boot must be disabled ! 

